reviewText: All 3 of these movies are very good.  Well written, well acted, good productions.  Trust me, I'm the first one to criticize a bad movie.  All of these are good.  Of course I like Jean Smart and Stockard Channing has never put a foot wrong in any movie.  These are stories that matter, that you can really get involved in.  I highly recommend this DVD
